original_title: Kaiser Chiefs: Live From Elland Road
overview: Brit rockers the Kaiser Chiefs are captured live in performance. Tracks include: 'Everything Is Average Nowadays', 'Every Day I Love You Less And Less', 'Heat Lies Down', 'Born To Be A Dancer', 'Can't Say What I Mean', 'Ruby', 'Saturday Night', 'Retirement', 'Oh My God' and many more.
title: Kaiser Chiefs: Live From Elland Road
